---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Team - Win-Win Apps"
  description="Meet the team behind Win-Win Apps. A Shopify merchant and a senior engineer building focused apps for real merchant problems."
  current="team"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Team</p>
      <h1>A merchant and a builder.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Win-Win Apps is a two-person team. We know the Shopify App Store from both sides of the dashboard.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-card-head">
          <div>
            <h3>Omar Shahban</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Co-Founder, CEO</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/omar-shahban/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-small">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
        <p>Omar has been a Shopify merchant for more than a decade. He co-founded <a href="https://gravid.ca" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gravid.ca</a> in 2017, a weighted blanket brand that has sold to over 60,000 Canadians and been featured on CBC, CTV, National Post and Financial Post. Across his merchant portfolio he has driven over $20M in global Shopify revenue across Canada, the US, the UK and Australia.</p>
        <p>Omar's decade as a merchant shapes every product decision at Win-Win Apps. Features, pricing and onboarding are designed around real merchant problems, not guesswork.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-card-head">
          <div>
            <h3>Shane Stratton</h3>
            <p class="team-role">Co-Founder, CTO</p>
          </div>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/shanestratton/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary btn-small">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
        <p>Shane brings over a decade of senior engineering experience, including roles at Amazon (Software Development Engineer II on Customer Engagement Technologies), IBM (WebSphere Commerce and SPSS Modeller) and Chess.com (fullstack development on the Variants project). At Win-Win Apps he leads production infrastructure, database design and the deployment pipeline.</p>
        <p>Shane's engineering discipline gives merchants a polished, reliable product while keeping operating costs low at portfolio scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <CTA
        heading="Have a question or an idea?"
        body="Merchant support, feature requests, press inquiries. Use the contact form and we will reply within 24 hours."
        primaryLabel="Contact us"
        primaryHref="/contact/"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.team-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--color-brown-outline);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 28px 30px;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.team-card-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.team-card-head h3 {
  margin: 0 0 4px;
  font-family: var(--font-serif);
  font-size: 24px;
  color: var(--color-blush-deep);
}
.team-role {
  margin: 0;
  color: var(--color-brown-secondary);
  font-size: 14px;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.team-card p {
  margin: 0 0 12px;
  color: var(--color-brown-primary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.team-card p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
.team-card a {
  color: var(--color-blush-deep);
}
.btn-small {
  padding: 8px 16px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
